<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الخَمْر <span class="c2">((١)</span>)<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>العنب.<span class="c5"> وفُسِّر به قوله:</span> <span class="c3">{إِنِّي أَرَانِي أَعْصِرُ خَمْراً}</span> <span class="c2">((٢)</span>)<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>ما أسكر من عصير العنب أو غيره<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>التَّخَوّف <span class="c2">((٣)</span>)<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>التَّنقص.<span class="c5"> وفُسِّر به قوله تعالى:</span> <span class="c3">{أَوْ يَأْخُذَهُمْ عَلَى تَخَوُّفٍ}</span> <span class="c2">((٤)</span>)<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
