<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span>السُّتور.<span class="c5"> وفُسِّر به قوله تعالى:</span> <span class="c3">{وَلَوْ أَلْقَى مَعَاذِيرَهُ}</span> <span class="c2">((١٤)</span>)<a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
